<span id="freeTextContainer54842852204696072"><strong>Touching and gripping novel</strong><br/><br/>this is a wonderful, touching novel of family, hardship, betrayal, and hope. I would recommend this book to all who enjoy intelligent fiction. 4.5 stars</span>

