<span id="freeTextContainer8718998176857170948">This is a beautifully written story in a setting that is uncommon for novels during this time period, where most World War I novels focus on Europe. I found the twists, reunions, and &quot;happy endings&quot; for various characters a bit too forced, which also left holes about some of those characters&apos; stories which did not quite add up. </span>
  <span id="freeText8718998176857170948" style="display:none">This is a beautifully written story in a setting that is uncommon for novels during this time period, where most World War I novels focus on Europe. I found the twists, reunions, and "happy endings" for various characters a bit too forced, which also left holes about some of those characters' stories which did not quite add up. </span>
